  "text": "`updated` is called but component wasn't updated (different from Vue 2)\n\n### Version\r\n3.0.0\r\n\r\n### Reproduction link\r\n[https://jsfiddle.net/7revor/xw0tLp65/42/](https://jsfiddle.net/7revor/xw0tLp65/42/)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\n1.Open the console.\r\n\r\n2.Click the update button.\r\n\r\n3.Observe the logging.\r\n\r\n### What is expected?\r\nChild component would not have updated.\r\n\r\n### What is actually happening?\r\nChild component updated.\r\n\r\n<!-- generated by vue-issues. DO NOT REMOVE -->",
